-----------------------------------------------------------Java Script-----------------------------------------------------
Programming Language and Scripting Language

Compiled Language


    HLL  ->  Compilation Stage  -> LLL


    Browser :
    ->Layout Engine(HTML,CSS is displayed because of Layout Engine in Web Browser)
    ->JS Engine(Interactivity and toperform operation)


    Data types:
    ->Primitives(Number of Primitives-7)(Pre Defined Data type in the language)(Lowest Level-Simple Data)
    ->-> Number (Integer,Float)
    ->-> String ('' or "" text in these quotes or double quotes considered as String)
    ->-> Boolean (can be True / False)
    ->-> BigInt 
    ->-> Undefined
    ->-> Null
    ->-> Symbol




    Console:
    ->REPL(Read Evaluate Print Loop)

    Variable:
    Used to define or give data a addres or location
    -->let<--(Automatically Datatype we donot need to define value thats why it create 2 bucket automatically use Indirect Addressing Mode thats why called it is Scripting Language)
    let myname='samarth';
    Storing as   Memory{myname}--->{samarth} (Indirect Addressing Mode)
    Rules to Define Variable:
    ->Cannot start with number
    ->a-z A-Z
    ->cannot use space( )
    ->cannot use keyword
    ->Special _ and $


    ---->Backticks(String templates)-->(`):(below esc n keywword);


